{"tid":452072,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"又到星期一，學校社工見聞錄","createTime":"2017-10-29T23:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-30T03:44:08.000Z","uid":112205,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7112ea3889495898aa844a363376d84e7addf240","tid":452072,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T23:59:44.000Z","msg":"各位同學早晨! 無錯，又係禮拜一呀!<br />\n星期一代表著既係咩? 就係要連續返五日你先可以再休息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實我的身份係一位學校社工，邊間就唔講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但就想藉依個機會，分享我在學校見到既kai人kai事和開心事<br />\n<br />\n話說我巡樓時，總係見到學生早上互抄功課<br />\n依個場面相當溫馨有愛，學生時代既大家總係無私、純真和有義氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見到學生抄功課，就隻眼開隻眼閉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n生活已經不容易，費事佢地又比訓導老師捉去喪罵。<br />\n<br />\n大家今個星期，又有咩打算，惗住點過呢?"},{"pid":"196790ff0ee0729ff38f79bbc6cb149263fd2a38","tid":452072,"uid":4647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T00:06:06.000Z","msg":"抄功課冇乜問題，被人抄的入咗U，抄人的做咗公務員"},{"pid":"da8de75af9fc4cee7e7a2a367523ac799df72a5b","tid":452072,"uid":4647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T00:12:16.000Z","msg":"仲有，玩外圍馬欠數被人打之後警司警戒，跟著攞博士學位，再做大學講師再做教授。學生仔點差，若是醒覺，將來會有好多機會"},{"pid":"795df2989af48c5c90313bc689c56a9a3eefe9b1","tid":452072,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T00:12:26.000Z","msg":"依個世界，做學生又點會冇試過抄功課<br />\n我自己都有抄和被抄啦，所以我覺得no big deal，不過要抄得醒。<br />\n<br />\n大學都係咁<br />\n人生的成就真係話唔埋"},{"pid":"5f67de07cded9372dcec7ab2d57efcbde3da4273","tid":452072,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T00:13:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有，玩外圍馬欠數被人打之後警司警戒，跟著攞博士學位，再做大學講師再做教授。學生仔點差，若是醒覺，將來會有好多機會</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n爸打玩外圍馬?"},{"pid":"0c823e146c7ecfc02c7b69996842afbad8731310","tid":452072,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T00:15:11.000Z","msg":"未來同行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學校社工 A仔位wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nfg入？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e4dd3f5db254ba3276017c23b332c30876957f","tid":452072,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T00:30:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未來同行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學校社工 A仔位wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nfg入？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想係a仔位，我係學校另外直接請<br />\n做到隻狗咁，地位、人工都低好多"},{"pid":"23a7656105bd1893271f868a081f5bee4f023abd","tid":452072,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:44:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>未來同行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學校社工 A仔位wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nfg入？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想係a仔位，我係學校另外直接請<br />\n做到隻狗咁，地位、人工都低好多</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有工番就好好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}